                "  Band            3 (       1575.0000m):        355.07247m distance",
                "  Band            4 (       1600.0000m):        355.07247m distance",
                "  Band            5 (       1625.0000m):        353.24445m distance",
                "  ...",
                "  Band           45 (       2625.0000m):        1514.0484m distance",
                "  Band           46 (       2650.0000m):        1402.8300m distance",
                "  Band           47 (       2675.0000m):        925.14042m distance",
                "  Band           48 (       2700.0000m):        844.82748m distance",
                "  Band           49 (       2725.0000m):        844.82731m distance",
                "Total distance covered (improved):        24744.877m",
                "Original glacier length:       23500.0m",
